ent-RMCJumpsuitMarineRoyal-name = royal crown marine uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitMarineRoyal-desc = The field uniform of the royal crown marines. They have shards of light Kevlar to help protect against stabbing weapons and bullets. Onpar with similar UNMC equipment.

