ent-RMCJumpsuitMarinePara-name = paramarine battle dress uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitMarinePara-desc = No.8 Pattern BDU used by the RCM's Paramarine regiments. Identical in cut and protection to standard issue uniforms, but issued in woodland camouflage. Lightweight Kevlar mesh offers limited protection against shrapnel and close-quarters threats.

