ent-RMCJumpsuitMarineParaService-name = paramarine service uniform
ent-RMCJumpsuitMarineParaService-desc = A formal No.2 service uniform worn by RCM-P officers. Features the same upper torso cut as the No.8 BDU, but paired with pressed khaki trousers. Issued for inspections, ceremonial duties, or when deployed in an advisory role.

